                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<section id="rules">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                <h2>The Rules of The Game: Season 2</h2>
                <p class="lead">As a professional engineering fraternity, we do not allow cheating.
                <p class="lead">Since it was snowing really hard last night, the game master has canceled all the outdoor activities.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Each team will have <a class="font-weight-bold">a team leader</a>, who is responsible for directly communicating with the game master if there are any problem or concern of the game.</li>
                    <li>Use the provided username and password to login to the system.</li>
                    <li>Each team has only <a class="font-weight-bold">two</a> hints. A team use their hint by contacting the game master via GroupMe.</li>
                    <li>Only when you enter the correct answer to the question will you be redirected to the next question.</li>
                    <li>Each team need <a class="font-weight-bold">at least an iphone and a laptop with Chrome installed</a> to succeed. The system is not built for mobile devices.</li>
                    <li>Turn on your laptop's audio. A pair of ear buds are recommended in case it gets noisy but not required.</li>
                    <li>The answer of each question contains mainly English characters(case-sensitive, only <strong>lower-case</strong> characters are allowed) and numbers, and possibly other characters(very uncommon).</li>
                    <li>If the system does not accept your answer, you are wrong. Do not ask the game master unless you are using your hints.</li>
                    <li>The first team that solve all problems win.</li>
                    <li>There are 9 Problems.</li>
                    <li>Have fun!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="author" class="bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto container">
                <h2>Author</h2>
                <p class="lead">Floyd Chen</p>
                <img class="img-fluid" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/floydchenchen/pictures/master/WechatIMG15.jpeg" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<% if (currentUser) { %>
<div class="text-center">
    <a class="btn btn-primary my-3" href="/p1" role="button">Start the Game!</a>
</div>
<% } %>

